OL,3,CMan dies in fire above barber's shop
OL,5,FA 27-year-old man has died after a
OL,6,Ffire above a barber's shop in
OL,7,FLincolnshire.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to
OL,10,FRopery Road, Gainsborough, at around
OL,11,F3.20am on Sunday.
OL,13,FThe victim died at the scene.
OL,15,FDamage could be seen to the roof of
OL,16,Fthe property, which is above the Top
OL,17,FCut barber's shop.
OL,19,FLincolnshire Police said the man's
OL,20,Ffamily had been informed.
