OL,3,CMan dies in fire above barber's shop
OL,5,FA spokesperson said: "We are working
OL,6,Fclosely with our colleagues at
OL,7,FLincolnshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,8,Fto fully understand what happened, and
OL,9,Fthe investigation is ongoing.
OL,11,F"Officers will remain on scene while
OL,12,Fenquiries continue."
